Crypt::NSS::X509 - A perl wrapper to the NSS X509 API
=====================================================

This library offers a wrapper around NSS providing a small, usable subset of the X509 
functionality of NSS.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

